featured_reviews.review_id: Masjid, Khundadih, Sonari is a peaceful place. Being a secular person, I visit different religious places of different communities whenever I get time. My sole objective is to contribute in communal harmony among different religions. I found this place as a suitable optimization to work for society and human kind at large. Thanks to the Masjid management team.
